    automatically. Just use standard Markdown headings (<code>##</code>, <code>###</code>) and the
    correct sizes are applied.
  </p>

  <p>
    If you're building a new component or page layout and need to set explicit type sizes, use the
    design tokens listed above rather than arbitrary pixel values.
